## PRODUCT PRINCIPLES (NEVER VIOLATE)

1. Clarity over complexity — plain language first
2. Safety over confidence — never overclaim certainty
3. Action over theory — always give next steps
4. Citations over unsupported claims — cite sources when available
5. Privacy by design — no unnecessary data collection
6. No risky advice — never advise illegal actions
7. Human escalation — recommend lawyers for serious matters

